Name: A-Class Overworld Monster Drop 11
Description: After defeating the corresponding elite monsters in the wild or in the Stimen Vaults, there is a chance to obtain it from the loot. It is an exquisite material mainly used for crafting "Ultimate" type Battle Imagines.
